<date box="[862,991,836,861]" pageId="9" pageNumber="582" value="1883" valueMax="1885">1883–1885</date>
; 
<date box="[1003,1132,836,860]" pageId="9" pageNumber="582" value="1889" valueMax="1890">1889–1890</date>
; 
<date box="[1145,1276,836,861]" pageId="9" pageNumber="582" value="1893" valueMax="1895">1893–1895</date>
). He соlleсted numerоus new inseсts in Centrаl Asiа, inсluding this new speсies.
</paragraph>
